<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.3">
<l>vañcaṉai ceyyat tāyuru vāki vantapē yalaṟimaṇ cēra</l>
<l>nañcamar mulaiyū ṭuyirceka vuṇṭa nātaṉait tāṉavar kūṟṟai</l>
<l>viñcaivā ṉavarcā raṇarcittar  viyantu</l>
<l>tuticey yappeṇṇu ruvāki</l>
<l>yañcuvai yamuta maṉṟaḷit tāṉait</l>
<l>tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who suckled from breasts full of poison when the life was destroyed</l>
<l>Of the demon who came having a mother’s form created in deceit,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that she met the earth, screaming,</l>
<l>[The one who is] Death to the Dānavas, the one who, having a girl’s form,</l>
<l rend="indent">once gave lovely sweet ambrosia,</l>
<l>So that wise celestials, heavenly messengers, and mystics, being in wonder,</l>
<l rend="indent">made praises, I saw in Tiruvallikkēṇi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
